# Svelte UI

## Framework

- Svelte 5 runes: `$state`, `$derived`, `$props` — see `App.svelte`, `ControlPanel.svelte`.
- Bootstrap 5 for layout, cards, buttons; theme tokens in `index.css` (`--st-*` variables).

## Parser debug UI

- `DataTable` + `DecodeStepRow` for step-by-step decode visibility.
- `ControlPanel`: load, step, reset, byte progress.

## File input (future)

Use `File` API + `ReadableStream` from `file.stream()`; yield to the UI between decode steps to keep interactions snappy. Avoid loading entire saves into memory when streaming path is available.

## Svelte MCP

Use the Svelte MCP server tools when creating or editing `.svelte` files (workspace plugin).

## Scope

Item tracker screens and maps are phase 2 — do not add until parser reaches full-save EOF on `SBS00.sav`.
